<tr>
<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Hi, My name is Bonesmacker and I have a few things I would like to see changed with my Shadow Knight, to not only make him a bring of death, but also the mean SOB that I would like to be. Now there is alot on this message board about Pally vs SK. If we are to be the counterparts of Paladins, or at least the anti paladin, well then perhaps they should change HT and LH to equal them out. How should they? Well how about change HT to either "demi" (a la Final Fantasy) the victim (bring the targets hp down by half) and then make the LH only bring the targets HP up to half. Then make both abilities unusable on any thing that cons red to you. I would like that a whole lot more than the current HT, however as a bring of death there is another little problem I have with our pets. I think that I would give up HT and all our spells if I could have a pet, that was equal to a necro at my level. With just a fear, and darkness spell, an equal level pet and me, and I would be totally happy with me and my class. Not like I am not already. So what do you think about that?<p>

<p>

Bonesmacker<br>
Troll/SK<br>
Povar</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
