<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Synthe, hits, misses, and average damage are based on dexterity. If that ranger has higher Dex than you, he will hit for max damage more often than you and his average will be higher (considering you have similar weapons). Most rangers put some points into dex, I would not be surprised if hit gets more max hits than you. So this is not really a class set thing, but a stat.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
