<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Bigguard,<br>
I could be wrong on this but damage is based on STR, not DEX. The higher STR you have the higher top and average damage you get.<br>
The server makes rolls on DEX when you have a weapon or spell that procs (eg.: Vamiric Embrace spell, DarkReaver sword). Also, higher DEX will allow you to learn fighting skills faster.<br>
Rangers have ultrahigh AGI. The higher AGI you have the less chance of being hit by a mob.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
